description.en-us: Featuring models, people and events of great significance throughout the history of the automobile. Each car came with an exclusive Hall of Fame Trading Card . This series was a Wal-Mart exclusive.

releases.notes: Small amount released at Mattel outlets. It was planned for 15k run, Target & Mattel had a falling out & series was stopped while the Chevelles were in production.
15k run, believed to be the same situation as the '70 Chevelle but needs to be verified.
Has 17th Annual Collector's Convention logo on roof. Limited to 700.
Has Hot Wheels Logo and Hall of Fame Sunday October 5th 2003 on roof. Limited to 1300.
Given to attendees of the Hall of Fame Grandstand event on November 11, 2003. Limited to 600.
